summary: AN ORDINANCE amending Plat 45W, Page 118, of the official Zoning Map to rezone property generally located in the Block bounded by S. Main St., 22nd Ave. S., 23rd Ave. S. and E. Yesler Way (except the Northwest Corner thereof) from RMH 350 to RM 800. (C.F. 287325 - Petition of Department of Community Development.)
